high_descs: Turn left at the window and walk to the tv.
Walk past the tv to the chair.
Bend down and pick up the pillow from the chair.  Spin around and turn right toward the couch.  Turn left at the couch and go to the far end of the couch.  Face the couch.
Put the pillow on the couch.
anns.task_desc: Move the pillow from the chair to the couch.

high_descs: Go to the yellow chair to your left.
Pick up the pillow on the yellow chair.
Turn around, step forward and then go to your right to go to the couch, then turn left and go to face the other end of the couch.
Place the pillow on the leftmost cushion of the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put a pillow on the couch.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to the yellow armchair containing a purple pillow.
Pick up the pillow from the armchair.
Turn around, walk slightly forward then turn right and walk to the blue sofa.
Put the pillow on the seat of the sofa which is on your left.
anns.task_desc: Move a pillow from an armchair to a sofa.
